## 7. Cost Architecture

| Agent | LLM Tier | Est. tokens/call | Est. cost/call |
|-------|----------|-------------------|----------------|
| Router | GPT-4o-mini | ~500 in + 50 out | $0.0001 |
| ProfileManager | GPT-4o | ~1500 in + 500 out | $0.015 |
| StudyPlanner | GPT-4o | ~2000 in + 800 out | $0.022 |
| MockInterviewer | GPT-4o | ~1500 in + 300 out | $0.012 |
| AnswerEvaluator | GPT-4o | ~2000 in + 600 out | $0.019 |
| StrategyAdvisor | GPT-4o | ~1500 in + 500 out | $0.015 |

**Estimated cost per full session** (~20 messages): $0.30 - $0.50

**Optimization levers**:
1. Router uses GPT-4o-mini (10x cheaper than GPT-4o)
2. Cache frequent routing patterns (same intent вҶ’ skip LLM call)
3. Summarize conversation history instead of passing full context
4. Token budget allocator prevents context window waste

