| API | FastAPI | Async, type-safe, auto-docs, production-ready |
| State Persistence | SQLite + SQLAlchemy | Lightweight, zero-infra for MVP, upgrade path to Postgres |
| Vector Store | FAISS (local) | Fast, no external dependency for MVP |
| Embeddings | Azure OpenAI ada-002 | Consistent with production stack |
| Testing | pytest + LLM-as-judge | Unit tests for logic, LLM eval for quality |
| Containerization | Docker + docker-compose | Reproducible, deployable |
| CI/CD | GitHub Actions | Free, integrated with repo |